Scaled Residual Deviance

Deviance Residual is scaled by dispersion, Phi. - for introducing deviance there is a sweet normal cancellation to sums of squares GLM book p24. - GLM boo p 33 for exponential family deviance/scaled deviance. - each observation’s contribution to the deviance? Deviance residual. - Calculation of Poisson deviance residual

resid(crime_fit, type="deviance")^2 %>% sum()

[1] 131256.9

Checks out with reported residual deviance above.
